T1  - From Local to Global: Offshoring and Asset Prices
AU  - Bretscher, Lorenzo
Y1  - 2022/04/18
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2023/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4393
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4393
T2  - Management Science
