TY  - JOUR
T1  - Capability Building in Sluggish Organizations
AU  - Eliaz, Kfir
AU  - Spiegler, Ran
Y1  - 2022/07/07
PY  - 2022
DA  - 2023/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2022.4445
